
Waffle ~%V BROWSE functions

<A>gain.....Re-read message      <N>ext.....Read next message
<B>ack......Back one message     <P>ost.....Enter a new message
<C>atch.....Mark ALL as read     <Q>uit.....Quit to main menu
<D>ownload..File transfer        <S>earch...By subject or author
<F>ollow....Post, with quotes    <U>njoin...Unsubscribe
<L>ist......Display subjects     <V>erbose..Redisplay with extras
<M>ail......Send private mail    <W>rite....Save to file

You can also enter a message's number to display it directly.
Keep hitting the <space> bar to continually read the next message.

Traditional commands can be prefixed with :'s -- type :? for a list.

